						<summary>

						<p>West wall of the same shrine.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājakēsarivarmaṉ</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Tribhº Vīrapāṇḍyadēva: Year 15 = 1280 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is incomplete. It records some grant to the servants of the temple of Vīrachōḷīśvaram-uḍaiyār in Koḻumam, by the citizens <hi rend="italic">(Nagarattār)</hi> of Eṟipaḍanallūr in Tuvarāpati-nāḍu of Oṟṟimmal in Uṟaiyūrkkūṟṟam in Irāśagaṁbhīra-vaḷanāḍu in Chōḷa-maṇḍalam. </p>						

